{"tid":448814,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【感動！】鼓勵隊友比入球慶祝更重要，福仔備受讚賞！","createTime":"2017-10-26T14:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T06:44:36.000Z","uid":114123,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6ade8513774bff71b75ce46811cf57037978389b","tid":448814,"uid":114123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"照常理黎講，當有球員取得入球後，其隊友都會蜂擁而至同佢一齊慶祝，除非係面對舊主或與入球隊友有心病先唔會慶祝。而曼聯年輕前鋒拉舒福特近日喺同史雲斯嘅比賽入面，就無同入球嘅連加特慶祝，究竟點解呢?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.images.dailystar.co.uk/dynamic/58/photos/995000/620x/Marcus-Rashford-654985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.dailystar.co.uk%2Fdynamic%2F58%2Fphotos%2F995000%2F620x%2FMarcus-Rashford-654985.jpg&h=630b40f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對史雲斯嘅聯賽盃入面，連加特喺上半場21分鐘成功取得入球，當大部份曼聯隊友都跑向呢位入球功臣之時，拉舒福特並無做相同嘅野，而佢係跑到隊友連迪洛夫身邊，原來佢係為左鼓勵呢位失意嘅隊友，希望佢可以振作起來!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=256239\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D256239&h=c2ece0cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連迪洛夫喺對上一輪英超面對升班馬哈特斯菲爾德時多次犯錯，導致曼聯落敗，其心情近日因此而跌至低谷。而深知連迪洛夫正一個人面對這黑暗期係非常困難的，拉舒福特見狀主動作出鼓勵，相信連迪洛夫一定會覺得好溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/nintchdbpict0003616606511.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fnintchdbpict0003616606511.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26w%3D960&h=176c3458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於拉舒福特嘅做法，一眾紅魔球迷都對佢有讚無彈，認為19歲嘅佢竟然可以咁成熟，實在令人感到安慰，再加上佢本身已擁有巨大嘅潛力，相信未來佢必定可以喺球壇取得超過人們想像嘅成就。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2-prod.mirror.co.uk/incoming/article11407091.ece/ALTERNATES/s615/MAIN-Manchester-Uniteds-English-midfielder-J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.mirror.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle11407091.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615%2FMAIN-Manchester-Uniteds-English-midfielder-J.jpg&h=5a5e2ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea743a36abec798c877e2b7362a5fff4a62a3dba","tid":448814,"uid":15745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf90e44e4164840d19724b50fc43872aaf982382","tid":448814,"uid":9284,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:41:53.000Z","msg":"安慰咪安慰<br />\n點解要掃人粒lin"},{"pid":"d514566f3f9f185c9c262ba9e89128ba821c5920","tid":448814,"uid":2153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>安慰咪安慰<br />\n點解要掃人粒lin</blockquote><br />\nAgger"},{"pid":"bb6d0913bc147c01c0700fd9264f2aa41cab8198","tid":448814,"uid":143629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"相對地路夫蘭就慘得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0f0e4bacce6e1c73b054ef40eebb723c9f2c06","tid":448814,"uid":31680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>安慰咪安慰<br />\n點解要掃人粒lin</blockquote><br />\n拉舒福特見狀主動作出鼓勵，<span style=\"color: red;\">相信連迪洛夫一定會覺得好溫暖</span>"},{"pid":"900a09d93faf3f66aff6216fa8db0802c7484c1c","tid":448814,"uid":21275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:50:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2804740f743f59ce5844b234a3d5a6776258aae6","tid":448814,"uid":51114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"俾個細自己幾年既後生仔安慰係咩感受"},{"pid":"33141bb96e613fa6956a96d384015e256c6c9d71","tid":448814,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"未來福隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor